sentences.en: Any shortage could push up grain prices.
sentences.cn: 任何短缺都会推动粮价上涨。

sentences.en: One absurd bid can push up prices for lots of people.
sentences.cn: 一次不合理的出价便能推升与许多人相关的价格。

sentences.en: Shops are no longer allowed to push up their prices whenever they want.
sentences.cn: 再不允许商店想什么时候提价就提价了。
